@page "/"

<PageTitle>My Utility Portal</PageTitle>

<style>
    .portal-card {
        border-radius: 20px;
        transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.2s ease-in-out;
        border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    .portal-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 1rem 3rem rgba(0,0,0,0.1) !important;
    }
    .icon-box {
        width: 70px; height: 70px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        margin: 0 auto 1.5rem auto;
    }
</style>

<div class="container py-5" style="max-width: 1100px;">
    <div class="text-center mb-5 pb-3">
        <h1 class="fw-bolder" style="color: #1e222d; font-size: 3rem; letter-spacing: -1px;">
            <i class="bi bi-grid-1x2-fill text-primary me-2"></i> My Utility Portal
        </h1>
        <p class="text-secondary fs-5 mt-3">일상을 혁신하는 나만의 강력한 도구 모음</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4 justify-content-center">
        
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm portal-card" style="background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1e222d 0%, #2b3240 100%);">
                <div class="card-body p-4 p-xl-5 text-center text-white">
                    <div class="icon-box" style="background-color: rgba(243, 186, 47, 0.15);">
                        <i class="bi bi-currency-bitcoin" style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: #f3ba2f;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">실시간 코인 분석기</h4>
                    <p class="text-light opacity-75 mb-4" style="font-size: 0.95rem;">
                        바이낸스 실시간 데이터를 바탕으로<br/>수학적 숏/롱 타점을 잡아냅니다.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/binance-chart" class="btn btn-warning w-100 fw-bold py-2 rounded-pill" style="color: #856404; background-color: #f3ba2f; border: none;">
                        차트 실행하기 🚀
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm portal-card bg-white">
                <div class="card-body p-4 p-xl-5 text-center">
                    <div class="icon-box" style="background-color: rgba(13, 110, 253, 0.1);">
                        <i class="bi bi-pie-chart-fill" style="font-size: 2rem; color: #0d6efd;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 text-dark">AI 금융 시뮬레이터</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-4" style="font-size: 0.95rem;">
                        1만 번의 평행우주 시뮬레이션으로<br/>6개월 뒤 자산의 미래를 예측합니다.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/finance" class="btn btn-primary w-100 fw-bold py-2 rounded-pill">
                        계산기 실행하기 📈
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm portal-card bg-white">
                <div class="card-body p-4 p-xl-5 text-center">
                    <div class="icon-box" style="background-color: rgba(25, 135, 84, 0.1);">
                        <i class="bi bi-braces" style="font-size: 2rem; color: #198754;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 text-dark">개발자 JSON 포맷터</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-4" style="font-size: 0.95rem;">
                        복잡한 JSON 데이터를 보기 좋게<br/>정렬하고 필요한 형태로 변환합니다.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/json" class="btn btn-success w-100 fw-bold py-2 rounded-pill">
                        툴 실행하기 💻
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm portal-card bg-white">
                <div class="card-body p-4 p-xl-5 text-center">
                    <div class="icon-box" style="background-color: rgba(13, 202, 240, 0.1);">
                        <i class="bi bi-terminal-fill" style="font-size: 2rem; color: #0dcaf0;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 text-dark">Regex & Cron 마스터</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-4" style="font-size: 0.95rem;">
                        머리 아픈 정규표현식을 실시간으로 테스트하고<br/>서버 스케줄러를 클릭으로 생성하세요.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/regexcron" class="btn btn-info text-white w-100 fw-bold py-2 rounded-pill">
                        툴 실행하기 ⚙️
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm portal-card" style="background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1e222d 0%, #0f172a 100%); border: 1px solid #2b3240;">
                <div class="card-body p-4 p-xl-5 text-center text-white">
                    <div class="icon-box" style="background-color: rgba(13, 202, 240, 0.15);">
                        <i class="bi bi-eye-fill" style="font-size: 2rem; color: #0dcaf0;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">고래 지갑 추적기</h4>
                    <p class="text-light opacity-75 mb-4" style="font-size: 0.95rem;">
                        비탈릭 부테린 등 세계 최고 부자들의<br/>이더리움 지갑 잔고를 실시간으로 훔쳐보세요.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/whale-tracker" class="btn btn-outline-info w-100 fw-bold py-2 rounded-pill border-2">
                        지갑 훔쳐보기 👀
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm portal-card bg-white" style="border: 2px solid #ffc107;">
                <div class="card-body p-4 p-xl-5 text-center">
                    <div class="icon-box shadow-sm" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd700, #ff8c00);">
                        <i class="bi bi-controller text-white" style="font-size: 2.2rem;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 text-dark">RPG 퀘스트 트래커</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-4" style="font-size: 0.95rem;">
                        매일의 일상을 게임처럼 즐겨보세요.<br/>할 일을 완료하고 경험치와 골드를 모아 레벨업!
                    </p>
                    <a href="/rpg-tracker" class="btn btn-warning text-dark w-100 fw-bold py-2 rounded-pill shadow-sm">
                        트래커 실행하기 🎮
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm portal-card bg-white" style="border-bottom: 4px solid #dc3545;">
                <div class="card-body p-4 p-xl-5 text-center">
                    <div class="icon-box shadow-sm" style="background-color: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.1);">
                        <i class="bi bi-arrow-left-right text-danger" style="font-size: 2.2rem;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 text-dark">김치 프리미엄 계산기</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-4" style="font-size: 0.95rem;">
                        업비트와 바이낸스 API를 연동하여<br/>국내외 코인 가격 차이를 실시간으로 추적합니다.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/kimchi-premium" class="btn btn-outline-danger w-100 fw-bold py-2 rounded-pill shadow-sm">
                        프리미엄 확인하기 💸
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm portal-card bg-white" style="border-right: 4px solid #7597de; border-bottom: 4px solid #2b1055;">
                <div class="card-body p-4 p-xl-5 text-center">
                    <div class="icon-box shadow-sm" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2b1055, #7597de);">
                        <i class="bi bi-suit-spade-fill text-warning" style="font-size: 2.2rem;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 text-dark">유희왕 덱 메이커</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-4" style="font-size: 0.95rem;">
                        글로벌 API 연동 테스트:<br/>전 세계 카드 데이터를 검색하고 나만의 덱을 구성합니다.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/yugioh-deck-maker" class="btn text-white w-100 fw-bold py-2 rounded-pill shadow-sm" style="background-color: #2b1055;">
                        듀얼 준비하기 🃏
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm portal-card bg-white" style="border-bottom: 4px solid #ff758c;">
                <div class="card-body p-4 p-xl-5 text-center">
                    <div class="icon-box shadow-sm" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff758c, #ff7eb3);">
                        <i class="bi bi-chat-heart-fill text-white" style="font-size: 2.2rem;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 text-dark">실시간 익명 방명록</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-4" style="font-size: 0.95rem;">
                        서버 메모리(Static)를 활용한 실시간 통신!<br/>DB 없이 접속자들과 메시지를 주고받아보세요.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/guestbook" class="btn text-white w-100 fw-bold py-2 rounded-pill shadow-sm" style="background-color: #ff758c;">
                        방명록 남기기 ✍️
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm portal-card bg-white" style="border-left: 4px solid #141e30;">
                <div class="card-body p-4 p-xl-5 text-center">
                    <div class="icon-box shadow-sm" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #141e30, #243b55);">
                        <i class="bi bi-shield-lock-fill text-success" style="font-size: 2.2rem;"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 text-dark">만능 암호화 툴박스</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-4" style="font-size: 0.95rem;">
                        Base64, URL 파싱, SHA-256 해시까지.<br/>개발자의 필수 유틸리티를 한곳에 모았습니다.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/crypto-toolbox" class="btn text-white w-100 fw-bold py-2 rounded-pill shadow-sm" style="background-color: #243b55;">
                        암호화 도구 열기 🔐
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>